tv.amwa.maj.io.mxf

Interface LocalTagEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, FixedLengthPack, MetadataObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalTagEntryImpl

    public interface LocalTagEntry
extends FixedLengthPack, MetadataObject, Cloneable

    Represents a single entry of the tag-to-key lookup table of a primer pack, mapping a 2 byte tag to a 16 byte key.

    See Also:
    PrimerPack.addLocalTagEntry(LocalTagEntry), PrimerPack.getLocalTagEntryBatch(), TypeDefinitions.LocalTagEntryReference, TypeDefinitions.LocalTagEntryBatch

short getLocalTag()
